erical experiments on two real data sets show that the proposed\nsemi-supervised clustering model using the WFTG is overall competitive with the\nstate-of-the-art methods developed in the literature of high-dimensional data\nclassification, and is superior to some of these methods.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 10 Nov 2014 22:08:23 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 13 Jun 2015 11:28:04 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 13 Aug 2015 19:49:33 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Tue, 6 Oct 2015 00:38:54 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-10-07"}
